snippet.title: Elon Musk denies having sexytime with Cara Delevingne and Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Elon Musk has denied that he had a ‘three-way affair’ with Cara Delevingne and Amber Heard. It has been alleged in a deposition from one of Amber’s friends in her ex-husband Johnny Depp’s lawsuit against her that the trio spent the night together in November 2016.  However, Musk, 48, has now hit back at the allegations, and also denied that he was involved with Heard, 34, while she was still married to Depp, 57.  In a statement to Page Six, the Tesla mogul said: ‘Cara and I are friends, but we’ve never been intimate. She would confirm this.


https://metro.co.uk/2020/06/19/elon-musk-denies-threesome-cara-delevingne-amber-heard-12873985/
